<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Votre Dossier Médical — SmartHealth AI</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { background: #f1f5f9; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #334155; }
        .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 32px auto; }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1d4ed8, #2563eb);
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
            padding: 32px 36px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header-app  { font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: white; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .header-sub  { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
        .header-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 14px;
            padding: 5px 16px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
        }

        /* Corps */
        .body { background: white; padding: 36px; }

        .greeting { font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .intro { font-size: 14px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }

        /* Card dossier */
        .dossier-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .dossier-card-header {
            background: #1d4ed8;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .dossier-card-title { display: table-cell; color: white; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: middle; }
        .dossier-card-id    { display: table-cell; text-align: right; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: middle; }
        .dossier-card-body  { padding: 20px; }

        .field { margin-bottom: 14px; padding-bottom: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
        .field:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none; }
        .field-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .field-value { font-size: 13px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6; }
        .field-empty { font-size: 13px; color: #cbd5e1; font-style: italic; }

        /* Alerte allergie */
        .allergy-box {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 10px 14px;
        }
        .allergy-warn { font-weight: bold; color: #991b1b; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .allergy-text { color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 13px; }

        /* Boutons */
        .btn-section { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 28px; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 4px;
        }
        .btn-primary { background: #7c3aed; color: white; }
        .btn-danger  { background: #dc2626; color: white; }
        .btn-info    { background: #0891b2; color: white; }

        /* Tech badges */
        .tech-section {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .tech-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; color: #0369a1; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .tech-badges { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
        .tech-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .tb-purple { background: #ede9fe; color: #6d28d9; }
        .tb-orange { background: #fff7ed; color: #c2410c; }
        .tb-green  { background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; }
        .tb-red    { background: #fef2f2; color: #b91c1c; }
        .tb-cyan   { background: #ecfeff; color: #0e7490; }

        /* Warning */
        .warning-box {
            background: #fffbeb;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #78350f;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 20px 36px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">

    {# ── HEADER ── #}
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-app">🏥 SmartHealth AI</div>
        <div class="header-sub">Système de gestion médicale — PIDEV 2025</div>
        <div class="header-badge">📧 Envoyé via Bundle PHPMailer</div>
    </div>

    {# ── CORPS ── #}
    <div class="body">

        <p class="greeting">Bonjour {{ user.prenom }} {{ user.nom }},</p>
        <p class="intro">
            Vous trouverez ci-dessous votre dossier médical <strong>#{{ dossier.id }}</strong>
            extrait de SmartHealth AI. Ce résumé vous est envoyé pour consultation et archivage personnel.
        </p>

        {# ── CARD DOSSIER ── #}
        <div class="dossier-card">
            <div class="dossier-card-header">
                <span class="dossier-card-title">📋 Dossier Médical</span>
                <span class="dossier-card-id">#{{ dossier.id }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="dossier-card-body">

                <div class="field">
                    <div class="field-label">📅 Date de création</div>
                    <div class="field-value">{{ dossier.dateCreation|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="field">
                    <div class="field-label">🔄 Dernière mise à jour</div>
                    <div class="field-value">{{ dossier.derniereMiseAJour|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</div>
                </div>

                {% if dossier.objectifSante %}
                <div class="field">
                    <div class="field-label">🎯 Objectif santé</div>
                    <div class="field-value">{{ dossier.objectifSante }}</div>
                </div>
                {% endif %}

                <div class="field">
                    <div class="field-label">📋 Antécédents médicaux</div>
                    {% if dossier.antecedentsMedicaux %}
                        <div class="field-value">{{ dossier.antecedentsMedicaux }}</div>
                    {% else %}
                        <div class="field-empty">Aucun antécédent renseigné</div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

                <div class="field">
                    <div class="field-label">🩺 Maladies chroniques</div>
                    {% if dossier.maladiesChroniques %}
                        <div class="field-value">{{ dossier.maladiesChroniques }}</div>
                    {% else %}
                        <div class="field-empty">Aucune maladie chronique renseignée</div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

                <div class="field">
                    <div class="field-label">⚠️ Allergies</div>
                    {% if dossier.allergies %}
                        <div class="allergy-box">
                            <div class="allergy-warn">⛔ ATTENTION</div>
                            <div class="allergy-text">{{ dossier.allergies }}</div>
                        </div>
                    {% else %}
                        <div class="field-empty">Aucune allergie connue</div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

                <div class="field">
                    <div class="field-label">💊 Traitements en cours</div>
                    {% if dossier.traitementsEnCours %}
                        <div class="field-value">{{ dossier.traitementsEnCours }}</div>
                    {% else %}
                        <div class="field-empty">Aucun traitement en cours</div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

                <div class="field">
                    <div class="field-label">🔬 Diagnostics</div>
                    {% if dossier.diagnostics %}
                        <div class="field-value">{{ dossier.diagnostics }}</div>
                    {% else %}
                        <div class="field-empty">Aucun diagnostic renseigné</div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        {# ── BOUTONS ── #}
        <div class="btn-section">
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">🤖 Analyse IA Groq</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger">📄 Télécharger PDF</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-info">🤗 Analyse HuggingFace</a>
        </div>

        {# ── BADGES TECH ── #}
        <div class="tech-section">
            <div class="tech-title">🛠️ Technologies intégrées dans SmartHealth AI</div>
            <div class="tech-badges">
                <span class="tech-badge tb-purple">🤖 IA 1 — Groq LLaMA 3.3</span>
                <span class="tech-badge tb-orange">🤗 IA 2 — Hugging Face</span>
                <span class="tech-badge tb-red">📄 DomPDF Bundle</span>
                <span class="tech-badge tb-green">📧 PHPMailer Bundle</span>
                <span class="tech-badge tb-cyan">🗺️ OpenStreetMap API</span>
                <span class="tech-badge tb-cyan">🧭 OpenRouteService API</span>
                <span class="tech-badge tb-green">🏥 MedlinePlus NIH API</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        {# ── AVERTISSEMENT ── #}
        <div class="warning-box">
            <strong>⚠️ Avertissement :</strong>
            Ce message et son contenu sont strictement confidentiels. Les informations médicales présentées
            ne remplacent pas un avis médical professionnel. Consultez votre médecin pour tout diagnostic.
            Email envoyé via <strong>Bundle PHPMailer</strong> (bundle externe Symfony).
        </div>

    </div>

    {# ── FOOTER ── #}
    <div class="footer">
        <strong>SmartHealth AI</strong> — Projet PIDEV 2025<br>
        Cet email a été envoyé à <strong>{{ user.email }}</strong><br>
        Ne pas répondre à cet email automatique.
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
